<li><span style="font-weight: 400;"> Once the terms are met, the buyer will release the payment.</span></li>
<li><span style="font-weight: 400;"> Buyers receive goods and are happy, and distributors/suppliers receive wire payment and are happy as well.</span></li>
</ul>
